.TH DISCVAULT 1 "" "discvault 0.4.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
discvault \- Linux CD archiver with CLI and Textual TUI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B discvault
[options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Rip and archive CDs to audio files and full disc images.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
show this help message and exit
.TP
\fB\-d\fR DEV, \fB\-\-device\fR DEV
CD device (default: auto\-detect)
.TP
\fB\-o\fR DIR, \fB\-\-base\-dir\fR DIR
Library base directory (overrides config)
.TP
\fB\-\-work\-dir\fR DIR
Temporary work directory (overrides config)
.TP
\fB\-\-tracks\fR SPEC
Track selection, e.g. 1\-10 or 1,2,4\-9
.TP
\fB\-\-metadata\-file\fR FILE
Import metadata from a .cue, .toc, .json, or .toml file
.TP
\fB\-\-metadata\-url\fR URL, \fB\-\-bandcamp\-url\fR URL
Import metadata from a supported page URL (Bandcamp albums or Discogs releases)
.TP
\fB\-\-artist\fR NAME
Artist name (overrides metadata lookup)
.TP
\fB\-\-album\fR NAME
Album name (overrides metadata lookup)
.TP
\fB\-\-year\fR YYYY
Album year (overrides metadata lookup)
.TP
\fB\-\-skip\-metadata\fR
Proceed without metadata lookup
.TP
\fB\-\-strict\-manual\-fallback\fR
Confirm before falling back to manual entry when lookup fails
.TP
\fB\-\-metadata\-timeout\fR SEC
Metadata lookup timeout in seconds (overrides config)
.TP
\fB\-\-metadata\-debug\fR
Print metadata provider debug output
.TP
\fB\-\-cli\fR
Force plain text CLI (default: TUI when interactive)
.TP
\fB\-\-check\-deps\fR
Check helper\-tool dependencies for the current selection and exit
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-cover\-art\fR
Disable downloading cover art
.TP
\fB\-\-keep\-wav\fR
Keep intermediate WAV files
.TP
\fB\-\-eject\fR
Eject disc when done
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be done without accessing the disc
.TP
\fB\-\-debug\fR
Print subprocess commands and verbose output
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
show program's version number and exit
.SH ENCODING
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-flac\fR
Skip FLAC encoding
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-mp3\fR
Skip MP3 encoding
.TP
\fB\-\-ogg\fR
Enable OGG Vorbis encoding (requires oggenc)
.TP
\fB\-\-opus\fR
Enable Opus encoding (requires opusenc)
.TP
\fB\-\-alac\fR
Enable ALAC encoding (requires ffmpeg)
.TP
\fB\-\-aac\fR
Enable AAC/M4A encoding (requires ffmpeg)
.TP
\fB\-\-wav\fR
Save final WAV copies in the library
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-verify\fR
Skip FLAC \-\-verify (faster but no integrity check)
.TP
\fB\-\-flac\-compression\fR N
FLAC compression level 0–8 (default: 8)
.TP
\fB\-\-mp3\-quality\fR N
lame \-V quality for VBR 0–9 (used when \-\-mp3\-bitrate=0)
.TP
\fB\-\-mp3\-bitrate\fR KBPS
lame CBR bitrate (default: 320; set 0 for VBR)
.TP
\fB\-\-opus\-bitrate\fR KBPS
Opus bitrate in kbps (default: config value)
.TP
\fB\-\-aac\-bitrate\fR KBPS
AAC bitrate in kbps (default: config value)
.SH DISC IMAGE
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-image\fR
Skip full disc image (cdrdao)
.TP
\fB\-\-iso\fR
Also export an ISO when the disc has a supported data track
.TP
\fB\-\-cdrdao\-driver\fR DRV
cdrdao driver override
.TP
\fB\-\-sample\-offset\fR SAMPLES
cdparanoia sample offset correction (overrides config)
.SH VERIFICATION
.TP
\fB\-\-accuraterip\fR
Enable optional AccurateRip verification if a helper is installed
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-accuraterip\fR
Disable AccurateRip verification even if enabled in config
